Charlotte Bobcats coach Larry Brown
stepped down today after meeting with owner Michael Jordan, the
National Basketball Association team said in a statement.  The Bobcats have 9 wins and 19 losses this season.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jay Beberman at 
 jbeberman@bloomberg.net  